** Designation / Job title : ** Developer Programmer - 261312/ Developer (Other) 

** Primary or Mandatory skills :- **

  * Good experience in Managed ServicesDelivery to agreed Service Levels. 
  * ITIL V3 minimum. 
  * Strong Experience and In Depth Understanding of Customer Domain in Banking and Insurance function. 
  * Experience in DataStage 11.x , ETL/DW concept 
  * AWS, OpenShift, ROSA ,Azure, KAFKA 
  * MDM, 
  * API Manager , Postman, API, Swagger, 
  * Jenkins, 
  * Netezza, Oracle, Redshift, DB2, 
  * Good Experience in SQL 
  * Good Communication, Analytical Skill 
  * ServiceNow 
  * Control M. 

** Good to have skills : **

  * CDC. 
  * Jira, Confluence. 

** Detailed Job description : - **

  * Responsible for managing Customer LOB team distributed across different geographical locations. 
  * Responsible for Managing all Batch Application, Data Delivery . 
  * Responsible for Application Availability for All critical API. 
  * Handling Prod and Non-Prod Platform Support. 
  * Managing Security vulnerability 
  * Responsible for Managing Critical Incident and other Critical data issue. 
  * Managing Customer escalation(s), New work transition, effort estimation. 
  * Responsible for regular operational and maintenance activity, coordination with different customer stakeholders in order to keep CSAT score high. 
  * Responsible for timely resolution of incoming request(s) in Customer LOB and assist team technically as and when needed. 
  * Responsible for fixing user query , Data issue , technical review , Effort estimation and Automation initiative. 
  * Interact with different team/person in order to fix user queries. 
  * Monitor and fix incoming Incident/Service request within defined SLA. 
  * Responsible for automation and other continuous improvement plan in Customer Experience LOB 
  * Status review meeting with respective audience. 

